{"tid":2216082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"電影檢查監督 商經局委派","createTime":"2020-09-24T12:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T12:09:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d121e90a60d1f5be3e521a88e2b2c5364b1d456d","tid":2216082,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:01:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/LV35OIAZFNEE3G4MS4KSABXLTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FLV35OIAZFNEE3G4MS4KSABXLTE%2F&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheK%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=ba4fcf2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FLV35OIAZFNEE3G4MS4KSABXLTE%2F&h=c17c925a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/LV35OIAZFNEE3G4MS4KSABXLTE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n電影檢查監督 商經局委派<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ONzfe73jaF91nMv69dVUfqF2vDM=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LGW4QT3A2BHRPP6ZTDH5XAWIPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FONzfe73jaF91nMv69dVUfqF2vDM%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLGW4QT3A2BHRPP6ZTDH5XAWIPE.jpg&h=5bc49535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■紀錄片中也有抗爭者的分化與互諒。<br />\n<br />\n根據《電檢條例》，電影檢查監督由商經局長委派的公職人員出任，現時由電影、報刊及物品管理專員出任，亦即本身為通訊事務總監的梁仲賢。回歸前他加入政府任職電訊工程師，之後晉升為總電訊工程師，2012年晉升為電訊管理局助理總監，三年後出任副總監（電訊），去年7月坐正。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：《理大圍城》再受打壓 送審DVD遭碎屍  崔允信︰荒謬事一單接一單<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n檢查員小組 特首委任<br />\n<br />\n通訊辦下設「電影、報刊及物品管理副專員」，由通訊事務副總監（廣播）的李若愚出任。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n電影報刊辦提及對《理大圍城》的決定來自電影檢查員的判斷，現行法例下設有一個電影檢查員小組，由特首不時委任人士組成，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"387f7d42bd4cb1d76ea75b3e3827bff7cde5222c","tid":2216082,"uid":216592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:09:22.000Z","msg":"荒謬事一單接一單"}]}